    "content": "LADIES' NIGHT (Bassline)\r\nAs recorded by Kool & The Gang\r\n(From the 1979 Album LADIES' NIGHT)\r\n\r\nWords and Music by George M. Brown & Kool And The Gang\r\nTranscribed by Slowhand\r\n\r\nGtr I (E A D G) - 'Robert \"Kool\" Bell - Bass'\r\n\r\n[tab] [Intro]\r\n Q=118\r\n 4/4\r\n  Gtr I\r\n   H    S E  S  E. S   W          H.       a  Q     +H     H\r\nG|-------------------|----------|---------16s18--|-(18)---------|\r\nD|-------------16\\---|----------|----------------|--------------|\r\nA|--------4/---------|----------|----------------|--------------|\r\nE|-------------------|----------|----------------|--------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n[tab]   H.      E E     Q.   E H      W          W          H.       Q\r\nG|--------------|--------------|----------|----------|---------------||\r\nD|--------------|--------------|----------|----------|---------------||\r\nA|--------------|-11\\----------|----------|----------|---------16\\---||\r\nE|-----------6/-|--------------|----------|----------|---------------||[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n[tab]     E E E E E S S +Q     e e e S S H     4x\r\nG||---------------------|-----------------||\r\nD||o-----2---4---6-(6)--|---------4------o||\r\nA||o-4------------------|-4-4-7-7--------o||\r\nE||---------------------|-----------------||[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n[tab] [Chorus]\r\n     E E E E E S S +Q     e e e S S H     4x\r\nG||---------------------|-----------------||\r\nD||o-----2---4---6-(6)--|---------4------o||\r\nA||o-4------------------|-4-4-7-7--------o||\r\nE||---------------------|-----------------||[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n[tab] [Verse 1]\r\n     E E E E E S S +Q     e e e S S H     4x\r\nG||---------------------|-----------------||\r\nD||o-----2---4---6-(6)--|---------4------o||\r\nA||o-4------------------|-4-4-7-7--------o||\r\nE||---------------------|-----------------||[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n[tab] [Chorus]\r\n     E E E E E S S +Q     e e e S S H     4x\r\nG||---------------------|-----------------||\r\nD||o-----2---4---6-(6)--|---------4------o||\r\nA||o-4------------------|-4-4-7-7--------o||\r\nE||---------------------|-----------------||[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n[tab] [Verse 2]\r\n     E E E E E S S +Q     e e e S S H     8x\r\nG||---------------------|-----------------||\r\nD||o-----2---4---6-(6)--|---------4------o||\r\nA||o-4------------------|-4-4-7-7--------o||\r\nE||---------------------|-----------------||[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n[tab] [Chorus]\r\n     E E E E E S S +Q     e e e S S H     4x\r\nG||---------------------|-----------------||\r\nD||o-----2---4---6-(6)--|---------4------o||\r\nA||o-4------------------|-4-4-7-7--------o||\r\nE||---------------------|-----------------||[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n[tab] [Bridge]\r\n     E. S E E E Q  S S   E Q  Q.   S S S S\r\nG||--------------------|-------------------|\r\nD||o-------------------|-------------------|\r\nA||o-------------------|------7----7-5-----|\r\nE||--5--5---3-5----5-6-|-7-------------8-7-|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n[tab]   E. S E E E Q  S S   E Q.   E E E E\r\nG|-------------------|------------------||\r\nD|-------------------|-----------------o||\r\nA|-------------------|--------7-7------o||\r\nE|-5--5---3-5----5-6-|-7----------7-7---||[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n [Outro]\r\n     |-3-|                                  |-3-|\r\n[tab]     Q Q Q Q  E S S   Q  +E  E Q  S S S S   Q Q Q Q  E S S   H    E E E E  6x\r\nG||-----------------|---------------------|----------------|---------------||\r\nD||o----------------|--------4-4--4-2-----|----------------|------4-4-----o||\r\nA||o-2-2---2----2-3-|-4--(4)----------4-3-|-2-2---2----2-3-|-4--------4-4-o||\r\nE||------4----------|---------------------|-----4----------|---------------||[/tab]\r\n\r\n************************************\r\nDuration Legend\r\n\r\nW - whole; H - half; Q - quarter; E - 8th; S - 16th; a - acciaccatura;\r\n+ - note tied to previous; . - note dotted;\r\nDuration letters will always appear directly above the note/fret number it represents\r\nthe duration for.  Duration letters with no fret number below them represent rests.\r\nUncapitalized letters represent notes that are staccato (1/2 duration).\r\n\r\n|  +()   -  note tied to previous\r\n|   /\\   -  slide into or out of (from/to \"nowhere\")\r\n|   s    -  legato slide\r\n| |-3-|  -  triplet\r\n|   |    -  bar\r\n|   ||   -  double bar\r\n|  ||o   -  repeat start\r\n|  o||   -  repeat end\r\n**************************************",
